# gluster
# You need one open port, starting at 24009 for each brick.
# This example opens enough ports for 20 storage servers and three bricks.
ACCEPT     sys:$ROOT           $FW       tcp      111
ACCEPT     sys:$ROOT           $FW       udp      111
ACCEPT     sys:$ROOT           $FW       tcp      24007:24047
ACCEPT     sys:$ROOT           $FW       tcp      38465:38467
